{"tid":1328816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打：社會衝突未見影響零售　短線未有明顯走資壓力","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:44:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74ae9982160f250b6fef7fa68e6317f36f07507f","tid":1328816,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"渣打大中華區高級經濟師劉健恒表示，未見近日社會衝突直接影響本地零售表現，又指零售市場2月起已持續收縮，主要受外圍不明朗因素及貿易摩擦影響。<br />\n<br />\n劉健恒說，本港消費情緒仍然有待利好消費刺激，例如貿易談判進展、聯儲局減息和中國已推出的刺激政策帶動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他提到，美國之前多次加息，香港最優惠利率亦只是調升0.125厘，因此相信即使聯儲局今年減息兩次，本港最優惠利率下行空間亦有限。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，港匯未見明顯轉弱，季節性因素過後，拆息亦已回復正常狀態，本港短線未見明顯走資壓力。"},{"pid":"4a1912b2de740fd394a5f60dbd3d15b6eacf3b87","tid":1328816,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469010-20190718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469010-20190718.htm&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakqarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=df619587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469010-20190718.htm&h=ec17de72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469010-20190718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2b9c052805ae160345b0476cdef60ebd8b34469c","tid":1328816,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2Kuooe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2Kuooe.png&h=50d005ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baiu7PV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbaiu7PV.png&h=c74f7ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TOGAiWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTOGAiWB.png&h=8f3de21b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9vmeuX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=